corpus = (
"Hello Students! Welcome to the NLP laboratory session 2026. "
"You can contact the instructor at xyz@kmv.edu.in or lab.support@kmv.org. "
"For urgent queries, call +919812311111 or 0987111110. "
"Course website: https://nlpxyz.edu/resources. "
"Topics include tokenization, stemming, lemmatization and regex. "
"Popular tags: #NLP #AI #TextMining. "
"Note: Some students wrote wrote duplicate words in assignments. "
"International examples: café, naïve, résumé. "
"Emoji feedback: 😊 👍 🐍. "
